WEBVTT

00:08.348 --> 00:10.122
<i>Previously, on</i>
"Ray Donovan"...

00:13.442 --> 00:15.054
Let me see
your fuckin' hands!

00:15.153 --> 00:16.507
Show me your fuckin' hands!
Hands!

00:24.188 --> 00:27.148
So if we pay him $9 million,

00:27.236 --> 00:30.125
he'll go ahead with the deal
at the lower price.

00:30.905 --> 00:32.240
I'll talk to my father.

00:39.140 --> 00:40.583
Fuckin'...

00:40.671 --> 00:42.296
Oh!

00:46.625 --> 00:48.185
You are fucking sorry!
Get the...

00:48.273 --> 00:50.482
‐ Get the fuck out!
‐ Ma'am, ma'am!

01:31.108 --> 01:32.296
Jim Sullivan?

01:33.203 --> 01:34.351
Look familiar?

01:43.743 --> 01:45.599
<i>Yes, I have
some information</i>

01:45.687 --> 01:47.091
<i>about Mickey Donovan.</i>

02:00.029 --> 02:02.242
